557
00:49:39,509 --> 00:49:41,374
Miss Yen, are you alright?

558
00:49:45,048 --> 00:49:46,379
I like that song you sing Wind Flower

559
00:49:47,451 --> 00:49:48,475
Will you sing it for me?

560
00:50:10,307 --> 00:50:16,678
Windflower, flying in the wind

561
00:50:17,381 --> 00:50:19,349
Sit down, how is it?
Had something to drink?

562
00:50:19,549 --> 00:50:20,072
A bit

563
00:50:20,117 --> 00:50:22,381
A bit isn't enough!
Come, get some more glasses

564
00:50:23,387 --> 00:50:24,581
You're all gotta drink

565
00:50:28,325 --> 00:50:29,053
Do you know her?

566
00:50:35,032 --> 00:50:36,693
You Hong Kong boys are real Romeos!

567
00:50:39,403 --> 00:50:42,133
Got your eyes on my girl
before the deals even done!

568
00:50:42,739 --> 00:50:45,071
Mr. Leong, you got it wrong,
we didn't mean it

569
00:50:45,542 --> 00:50:47,203
We just like her singing

570
00:50:47,778 --> 00:50:50,338
I also heard, you wanted
to take her with you!

571
00:50:56,420 --> 00:50:58,047
She's my trump card,

572
00:50:58,989 --> 00:51:01,116
I spent a lot of time grooming her

573
00:51:02,492 --> 00:51:03,618
Mr. Leong, you got it wrong

574
00:51:05,362 --> 00:51:07,421
We already liked Sally
when we were in Hong Kong

575
00:51:08,632 --> 00:51:10,122
Loved her singing

576
00:51:11,268 --> 00:51:13,668
We were staring at her
because it was strange

577
00:51:14,704 --> 00:51:16,672
She seemed to have changed!

578
00:51:17,474 --> 00:51:18,805
She's not beautiful any more

579
00:51:19,109 --> 00:51:19,438
Ben!

580
00:51:19,643 --> 00:51:20,701
She's lost her innocence

581
00:51:23,080 --> 00:51:24,206
She's not happy anymore

582
00:51:27,150 --> 00:51:28,515
What sort of grooming is that?

583
00:51:30,387 --> 00:51:31,547
Are you accusing me?

584
00:51:34,458 --> 00:51:37,359
No one else dares to
talk to me like that!

585
00:51:40,831 --> 00:51:42,321
Young man, you've got guts!

586
00:51:43,066 --> 00:51:43,691
Bring the booze

587
00:51:50,307 --> 00:51:52,138
Let's empty the bottle

588
00:52:04,154 --> 00:52:05,178
I made the screw up, it's my fault!

589
00:52:08,291 --> 00:52:09,053
I'll drink!

590
00:52:31,114 --> 00:52:32,445
Right! Real buddies!

591
00:52:33,150 --> 00:52:34,447
Since you're buddies,

592
00:52:34,751 --> 00:52:36,218
all three of you drink!

593
00:52:43,226 --> 00:52:44,887
Ben! What are you doing?
You call yourself our pal?

594
00:52:45,095 --> 00:52:45,527
Don't let him step on us!

595
00:52:46,730 --> 00:52:47,594
Aren't you being selfish?

596
00:52:47,864 --> 00:52:50,128
Don't let him step on us!
What did you say?

597
00:52:50,834 --> 00:52:53,098
You screwed up,

598
00:52:53,270 --> 00:52:54,294
don't drag me into it!

599
00:52:58,542 --> 00:52:59,474
I did that for all of us

600
00:53:01,144 --> 00:53:01,633
Stop it!

601
00:53:04,381 --> 00:53:05,541
What are you two fighting about?

602
00:53:10,187 --> 00:53:11,245
You hit me?

603
00:53:11,321 --> 00:53:12,151
Serves you bleeding right!

604
00:53:25,735 --> 00:53:26,292
Ben!

605
00:53:28,471 --> 00:53:29,199
You traitors!

606
00:53:31,208 --> 00:53:31,867
Bastard

607
00:53:34,244 --> 00:53:34,642
Watch over Ben

608
00:53:38,248 --> 00:53:39,442
Old shithead! Pull him up!

609
00:53:40,150 --> 00:53:40,639
Run!

610
00:53:42,152 --> 00:53:44,382
Run! Quick!

611
00:53:56,700 --> 00:53:59,260
Go back, quickly!
Let me go, let me go...

612
00:54:00,203 --> 00:54:00,692
Don't come over!

613
00:54:00,904 --> 00:54:02,303
Don't move! Or I'll kill him!

614
00:54:07,277 --> 00:54:07,971
One step more and I'll shoot!

615
00:54:08,478 --> 00:54:10,275
Help! Don't come over!

616
00:54:10,480 --> 00:54:11,640
Kill them!

617
00:54:21,258 --> 00:54:22,225
Let me go or you'll die!

618
00:54:22,259 --> 00:54:24,193
Ben, where are you going?

619
00:54:24,227 --> 00:54:24,693
Ben

620
00:54:30,300 --> 00:54:33,394
Bitch! You're not going any where!

621
00:54:39,509 --> 00:54:40,271
Sally!

622
00:54:41,945 --> 00:54:43,913
Ben, Frank!

623
00:54:44,281 --> 00:54:45,339
Help! Quick!

624
00:54:51,621 --> 00:54:52,883
Don't move. Let me go

625
00:54:53,523 --> 00:54:57,516
Sally, Sally

626
00:54:59,863 --> 00:55:01,763
Will we make it?

627
00:55:02,766 --> 00:55:04,358
Let's go now?

628
00:55:06,803 --> 00:55:07,360
Watch out!

629
00:55:36,333 --> 00:55:38,358
Are you guys crazy?
Stuck with this dame

630
00:55:38,635 --> 00:55:39,727
Do you wanna get us killed?

631
00:55:40,704 --> 00:55:43,264
I promised her I'd take her away

632
00:55:43,540 --> 00:55:45,599
That's your dame business,
leave me out

633
00:55:45,842 --> 00:55:46,934
Stop it Paul!

634
00:55:47,477 --> 00:55:48,409
If we're still buddies

635
00:55:48,778 --> 00:55:49,710
It's not important

636
00:55:49,913 --> 00:55:50,504
Let's get the hell out first!

637
00:55:50,747 --> 00:55:52,408
No way! You'll never leave!

638
00:55:52,449 --> 00:55:53,279
Stop fighting!

639
00:55:59,422 --> 00:55:59,820
Get down

640
00:56:03,760 --> 00:56:05,887
The gold leaves, where is it?

641
00:56:07,397 --> 00:56:08,728
Luke! Where is the gold?

642
00:56:08,865 --> 00:56:09,627
Where's Sally's passport?

643
00:56:10,467 --> 00:56:10,899
I don't know

644
00:56:11,835 --> 00:56:13,928
You said it was here! Where's the gold?

645
00:56:14,938 --> 00:56:15,802
In the safe

646
00:56:15,972 --> 00:56:17,405
Where is Sally's passport?

647
00:56:17,474 --> 00:56:18,441
You'll get it over my dead body

648
00:56:30,987 --> 00:56:32,011
Where the hell is Sally's passport?

649
00:56:33,356 --> 00:56:33,947
Speak up!

650
00:56:34,457 --> 00:56:35,355
You'll have to kill me first!

651
00:56:35,558 --> 00:56:36,456
I bet it's in the safe

652
00:56:37,360 --> 00:56:39,328
Bastards! You won't get of here alive

653
00:56:44,968 --> 00:56:47,129
Sally, don't worry

654
00:56:47,337 --> 00:56:49,464
Ben will help you,
even without your passport

655
00:56:49,572 --> 00:56:50,834
We could be refuges,

656
00:56:51,074 --> 00:56:52,905
sneak over to Hong Kong

657
00:57:15,064 --> 00:57:15,496
Sally

658
00:57:22,539 --> 00:57:24,598
You see! I told you not to worry

659
00:57:24,874 --> 00:57:27,001
We'll get back to Hong Kong, right?

660
00:57:28,378 --> 00:57:30,403
Hey! Release Mr. Leong

661
00:57:47,464 --> 00:57:48,055
Take your clothes off

662
00:57:54,838 --> 00:57:56,738
Not Mr. Leong, he's our brother

663
00:58:58,868 --> 00:58:59,562
Where's my passport?

664
00:59:03,506 --> 00:59:04,905
My passport's gone!

665
00:59:05,475 --> 00:59:06,567
Sally keep cool!

666
00:59:15,151 --> 00:59:16,743
Bitch!

667
00:59:20,523 --> 00:59:20,784
Sally!

668
00:59:21,291 --> 00:59:21,882
Stay away

669
00:59:23,493 --> 00:59:24,517
Help!

670
00:59:26,262 --> 00:59:27,661
Bastards! Don't touch my gold!

671
00:59:29,699 --> 00:59:32,532
How dare you take my gold! My gold!

672
00:59:33,102 --> 00:59:34,660
You can't, give it back...

673
00:59:34,837 --> 00:59:35,565
Let her go!

674
00:59:36,072 --> 00:59:37,767
Okay! I'll let her go

675
00:59:40,510 --> 00:59:41,568
Sally!

676
00:59:48,551 --> 00:59:49,017
Sally!

677
01:00:08,304 --> 01:00:08,895
Don't move!

678
01:00:09,672 --> 01:00:10,331
Stay away!

679
01:00:10,540 --> 01:00:11,632
Or I'll kill them

680
01:00:21,684 --> 01:00:22,912
Don't move! Wanna die?

681
01:00:23,119 --> 01:00:24,552
This is Vietnam, you won't get out alive!

682
01:00:26,122 --> 01:00:27,350
Come on! You shut up!

683
01:00:29,659 --> 01:00:31,718
Punk, you won't get out of Saigon!

684
01:00:31,995 --> 01:00:32,586
No way!

685
01:00:33,029 --> 01:00:33,961
Shut up!

686
01:00:34,597 --> 01:00:35,291
Drive, just go on!

687
01:00:35,598 --> 01:00:37,623
Go on! Quickly

688
01:00:39,035 --> 01:00:39,592
Come on!

689
01:00:41,270 --> 01:00:42,202
Drive on!

690
01:00:52,715 --> 01:00:56,378
Ben, get in, quick, quick!

691
01:00:59,355 --> 01:01:01,323
Don't let them get away

692
01:01:01,691 --> 01:01:03,921
You must get them

693
01:01:04,060 --> 01:01:05,652
Get in, quick, quick!

694
01:01:15,171 --> 01:01:16,968
You'll be alright! Don't worry!

695
01:01:33,423 --> 01:01:34,048
What do we do?

696
01:01:37,727 --> 01:01:40,389
Don't worry, I used to work for the CIA,
I'll handle it

697
01:01:44,867 --> 01:01:45,731
What are you doing here?

698
01:01:46,035 --> 01:01:47,798
Sorry sir, I have a pass

699
01:01:49,372 --> 01:01:50,304
Sir, what's going on?

700
01:01:51,040 --> 01:01:53,065
We're being attacked by Vietcongs,
it's dangerous here

701
01:01:53,342 --> 01:01:54,001
You better get out of here

702
01:01:54,377 --> 01:01:55,742
One of our friends is seriously hurt

703
01:01:55,778 --> 01:01:57,245
We must move her to another town urgently

704
01:01:58,715 --> 01:01:59,704
Okay, but take care

705
01:01:59,916 --> 01:02:00,280
Thanks

706
01:02:00,450 --> 01:02:00,916
Let them pass

707
01:02:33,750 --> 01:02:36,412
Can't turn back now!
Let's just get through! Quick!

708
01:02:58,274 --> 01:02:59,764
Help me, take me...

709
01:02:59,809 --> 01:03:02,778
What are you doing? Go away, piss off...

710
01:03:02,812 --> 01:03:05,110
Piss off, go, get lost!

711
01:03:16,726 --> 01:03:17,192
They're so pitiful

712
01:03:39,749 --> 01:03:41,239
Move, move! Bastards!

713
01:03:43,986 --> 01:03:44,975
Drive on, faster!

714
01:04:15,151 --> 01:04:16,880
Frank, start from there,

715
01:04:16,919 --> 01:04:18,819
plant a mine every there steps in case

716
01:04:19,055 --> 01:04:19,453
Right!

717
01:04:19,589 --> 01:04:20,055
Quickly!

718
01:04:42,044 --> 01:04:42,874
You okay?

719
01:04:54,023 --> 01:04:54,921
Hang on

720
01:04:55,892 --> 01:04:56,517
You'll be okay

721
01:04:59,929 --> 01:05:01,396
Will we make it?

722
01:05:02,398 --> 01:05:06,129
We'll get away! The boat will
leave soon, don't worry

723
01:05:07,837 --> 01:05:08,565
Really?

724
01:05:10,106 --> 01:05:11,971
Really! Believe me

725
01:05:13,910 --> 01:05:16,435
I told you, once we have
the change to leave

726
01:05:16,946 --> 01:05:18,140
We'll go back to Hong Kong together

727
01:05:20,917 --> 01:05:21,884
Be strong

728
01:05:25,054 --> 01:05:26,021
You'll make it back to Hong Kong

729
01:05:27,123 --> 01:05:29,489
I've got a record of yours at home
Waiting to be autographed

730
01:05:36,966 --> 01:05:39,958
Hey! Luke, is this boat coming?

731
01:05:40,569 --> 01:05:42,969
If those Vietnam bastards get here,
we'll be dead!

732
01:05:43,139 --> 01:05:44,003
Is that boat for real?

733
01:05:46,208 --> 01:05:48,233
Hey! What do you want?

734
01:05:49,011 --> 01:05:50,239
Answer me okay?

735
01:05:50,413 --> 01:05:56,318
Are you human? Spare a thought for us

736
01:05:57,486 --> 01:05:59,386
You only care about your gold,
what about us?

737
01:06:00,056 --> 01:06:01,546
Are you blind? Can't you see?

738
01:06:06,195 --> 01:06:06,923
Frank!

739
01:06:09,398 --> 01:06:10,057
What are you doing?

740
01:06:11,000 --> 01:06:12,399
I feel like shit!

741
01:06:29,585 --> 01:06:30,483
Ben, the boat's here!

742
01:06:34,490 --> 01:06:35,457
Why did it take so long?

743
01:06:35,691 --> 01:06:39,388
Last night there was a Vietcong
attack, it's dangerous

744
01:06:40,162 --> 01:06:41,993
Stop the boat up front first

745
01:06:42,164 --> 01:06:44,189
Up front... Up front...

746
01:06:44,533 --> 01:06:47,024
Sally, the boat! The boat's here!

747
01:07:46,162 --> 01:07:47,652
Hey! Stop the boat! Stop! Stop!

748
01:07:48,030 --> 01:07:49,361
Can't stop! It's too dangerous!

749
01:07:55,171 --> 01:07:57,696
Stop! Wait for me! Wait for me!

750
01:07:59,608 --> 01:08:00,768
I can't wait for you!

751
01:08:14,457 --> 01:08:15,355
Go on! No! come on!

752
01:08:15,624 --> 01:08:16,420
Go on! I'll give you gold!

753
01:08:17,460 --> 01:08:18,188
Help me please!

754
01:08:19,395 --> 01:08:20,020
Come on!

755
01:08:26,268 --> 01:08:28,395
Like this! Okay! Come on, quickly...

756
01:08:28,771 --> 01:08:31,239
Ben, I'll cover you,
get on the boat, quick!

757
01:08:49,258 --> 01:08:50,190
Paul

758
01:09:01,103 --> 01:09:02,798
Ben! Quick! Quick!

759
01:09:06,742 --> 01:09:07,572
Wait!

760
01:09:39,675 --> 01:09:41,233
Sally, Sally...

761
01:09:51,253 --> 01:09:54,916
Sally, Sally...

762
01:10:03,766 --> 01:10:06,291
They're catching up!
Luke, get on the boat! Luke!

763
01:10:07,670 --> 01:10:09,137
Luke, Luke!

764
01:10:09,705 --> 01:10:11,172
Go, Luke

765
01:10:11,373 --> 01:10:13,238
Let her go, let go now!

766
01:10:14,310 --> 01:10:15,299
Get on the boat, Luke!

767
01:11:18,907 --> 01:11:20,204
Shit! Why doesn't the boat move?

768
01:11:22,745 --> 01:11:23,370
God damn!

769
01:11:24,280 --> 01:11:25,645
Hey! Give us a hand now!

770
01:11:26,682 --> 01:11:28,343
If those damn Vietcong get us we're dead!

771
01:11:32,721 --> 01:11:35,485
God damn it! Aren't you guys worried?
The boat's screwed!

772
01:11:36,292 --> 01:11:37,589
Come and help!
Stop sitting there like statues?

773
01:11:38,494 --> 01:11:39,893
Luke, can you fix it?

774
01:11:42,831 --> 01:11:44,423
I know you're upset over Sally's death,

775
01:11:44,566 --> 01:11:45,260
so am I!

776
01:11:46,335 --> 01:11:48,326
But it's better this way?
She won't drag us down!

777
01:11:49,271 --> 01:11:50,397
We're scared shitless

778
01:11:50,873 --> 01:11:51,305
not knowing how much longer we'll die

779
01:11:51,473 --> 01:11:52,030
Isn't that worse?

780
01:11:53,275 --> 01:11:53,764
If this boat sinks,

781
01:11:54,576 --> 01:11:56,441
we'll lose all this gold

782
01:12:03,786 --> 01:12:05,310
Hey! Don't touch my gold!

783
01:12:06,422 --> 01:12:08,481
Hey, Ben, put it back!

784
01:12:09,291 --> 01:12:11,589
Hey! Stop doing that, or I'll shoot!

785
01:12:12,628 --> 01:12:13,356
Come on!

786
01:12:14,396 --> 01:12:16,591
Put the gold down!

787
01:12:17,633 --> 01:12:18,292
Are you crazy?

788
01:12:19,501 --> 01:12:21,901
Go on! If you shoot
I'll blow your head up!

789
01:12:22,838 --> 01:12:23,770
For me I'm already dead,

790
01:12:24,273 --> 01:12:25,399
but I don't want to lose the gold

791
01:12:31,480 --> 01:12:32,378
Frank, put the gun done

792
01:12:34,550 --> 01:12:35,608
Put the gun down!

793
01:12:42,391 --> 01:12:44,052
Are you putting this gold
before your friends?!

794
01:12:45,994 --> 01:12:47,825
Do you still know what friends are?

795
01:12:48,997 --> 01:12:49,895
Do you know what you're doing?

796
01:12:51,767 --> 01:12:54,099
You're pointing your gun
at a buddy of over 10 years!

797
01:12:56,972 --> 01:12:58,405
Do you measure your friendship in gold?

798
01:13:01,110 --> 01:13:01,769
Is this enough?

799
01:13:06,648 --> 01:13:08,513
Over 10 years of friendship...

800
01:13:09,918 --> 01:13:11,385
That friendship is over,

801
01:13:11,520 --> 01:13:12,452
we're not friends anymore

802
01:13:13,021 --> 01:13:13,715
Shoot then!

803
01:13:14,089 --> 01:13:15,386
I've known you for over 10 years

804
01:13:18,427 --> 01:13:20,418
Over 10 years!
If you want you can kill me!

805
01:13:20,796 --> 01:13:22,627
Shoot! Go on shoot...

806
01:13:22,998 --> 01:13:26,126
Please stop throwing it away!
I'm sorry!

807
01:13:27,002 --> 01:13:28,663
That's all I'm asking for

808
01:13:29,605 --> 01:13:31,334
All I want in this life is simple

809
01:13:32,841 --> 01:13:34,809
Just this box of gold, is that too much?

810
01:13:53,429 --> 01:13:54,418
This boat is sinking

811
01:13:55,831 --> 01:13:57,628
We better do something about it?

812
01:14:03,806 --> 01:14:04,500
Do you want to die?

813
01:14:04,706 --> 01:14:05,695
I want my gold!

814
01:14:05,908 --> 01:14:06,704
Let's jump!

815
01:14:07,042 --> 01:14:08,134
Quick jump!

816
01:14:25,394 --> 01:14:29,728
The gold, the gold...

817
01:14:40,909 --> 01:14:42,103
Paul

818
01:14:44,646 --> 01:14:45,203
My gold!

819
01:14:45,481 --> 01:14:47,039
Paul, come on now, Ah!

820
01:14:48,484 --> 01:14:49,212
Come on now!

821
01:14:56,425 --> 01:14:58,484
I found it, I found the gold!

822
01:14:58,527 --> 01:15:00,586
Paul, are you crazy! Paul!

823
01:15:06,168 --> 01:15:07,032
Paul

824
01:15:10,038 --> 01:15:10,902
Help!

825
01:15:13,008 --> 01:15:13,736
Go and help him

826
01:15:14,076 --> 01:15:17,204
I can't make it!
Help me! Help!

827
01:15:18,247 --> 01:15:21,478
Help me... Help!

828
01:15:22,484 --> 01:15:23,576
The gold's too heavy...

829
01:15:29,725 --> 01:15:30,248
The gold...

830
01:15:30,559 --> 01:15:32,584
You wanna die? Forget about the gold!

831
01:15:32,895 --> 01:15:33,623
Let's go!

832
01:15:56,084 --> 01:15:56,743
Don't you wanna live?

833
01:15:59,888 --> 01:16:03,119
