to go to Hong Kong

1105
01:52:05,785 --> 01:52:06,809
The world is changing...

1106
01:52:08,588 --> 01:52:12,718
I'm used to my own way of life

1107
01:52:13,460 --> 01:52:14,552
All of a sudden, I have to make a change

1108
01:52:15,829 --> 01:52:16,887
I just can't...

1109
01:52:17,697 --> 01:52:18,686
I've got to go back!

1110
01:52:19,833 --> 01:52:21,232
That's my home!

1111
01:52:27,040 --> 01:52:28,268
It's a long way to go...

1112
01:52:28,708 --> 01:52:29,697
I've got to go back!

1113
01:52:33,213 --> 01:52:33,679
Take care!

1114
01:52:34,848 --> 01:52:35,507
Take care!

1115
01:54:07,473 --> 01:54:08,201
Sugar cane juice...

1116
01:54:08,575 --> 01:54:09,337
60 cents pleases...

1117
01:54:11,277 --> 01:54:14,041
He's not feeling so well these days...

1118
01:54:14,314 --> 01:54:18,375
Be good, eat something...

1119
01:54:19,219 --> 01:54:19,913
Be good

1120
01:54:21,688 --> 01:54:22,620
Come on

1121
01:55:01,995 --> 01:55:05,590
Ben! You're back, great...!

1122
01:55:18,211 --> 01:55:19,178
His name is Frank

1123
01:55:51,711 --> 01:55:53,542
Boss, Mr King says he's
ready for the meeting!

1124
01:55:55,581 --> 01:55:56,741
I think it's time for me to retire

1125
01:55:57,784 --> 01:55:59,046
The world belong to the young people

1126
01:56:00,320 --> 01:56:02,788
Paul is a very capable person

1127
01:56:03,456 --> 01:56:04,548
We made money,

1128
01:56:05,391 --> 01:56:07,154
we spent all...!

1129
01:56:07,593 --> 01:56:09,288
Even the government could
not lay a finger on us!

1130
01:56:09,862 --> 01:56:11,921
Have guts, and friend enough!

1131
01:56:13,399 --> 01:56:15,333
I seldom make a wrong choice!

1132
01:56:16,669 --> 01:56:19,502
Paul will be the most suitable successor!

1133
01:56:22,842 --> 01:56:23,240
Congratulations...

1134
01:56:23,409 --> 01:56:24,808
Thank you, Mr. King...

1135
01:56:24,978 --> 01:56:25,706
I'll try my best to fulfill my duties...

1136
01:56:27,080 --> 01:56:28,342
I won't disappoint you!

1137
01:56:28,815 --> 01:56:31,375
I have never disappointed myself...

1138
01:56:36,889 --> 01:56:37,685
Congratulations, Paul

1139
01:56:37,957 --> 01:56:38,548
Thank you

1140
01:56:39,425 --> 01:56:41,893
An old friend of Paul

1141
01:56:42,095 --> 01:56:43,119
wants to see him!

1142
01:56:43,563 --> 01:56:45,531
Okay...anyway. We're through!

1143
01:56:45,999 --> 01:56:46,590
Show him in...!

1144
01:56:46,866 --> 01:56:47,389
Yes

1145
01:57:05,118 --> 01:57:06,949
Ben, when did you come back?

1146
01:57:09,889 --> 01:57:11,379
Let me introduce, Mr. King!

1147
01:57:12,225 --> 01:57:13,522
Mr. King, this is Ben,

1148
01:57:13,993 --> 01:57:15,119
my old friend

1149
01:57:15,728 --> 01:57:17,389
He stickled with me throughout
my time in Vietnam

1150
01:57:17,897 --> 01:57:20,764
So thrilled to see you again, really!

1151
01:57:21,934 --> 01:57:23,333
I'm so happy to see you...!

1152
01:57:25,171 --> 01:57:27,264
Half of mine is yours!

1153
01:57:29,976 --> 01:57:30,772
What about Frank?

1154
01:57:31,444 --> 01:57:31,933
Frank?

1155
01:57:34,747 --> 01:57:39,343
He kept telling us to leave him
behind when he was wounded alone

1156
01:57:40,186 --> 01:57:41,414
And go with you to Hong Kong

1157
01:57:42,889 --> 01:57:45,687
I wanted to help him,
but I was badly wounded

1158
01:57:46,492 --> 01:57:49,791
I was so up set,
yet I have done my best!

1159
01:57:51,864 --> 01:57:53,661
When we went to Vietnam
to try our luck!

1160
01:57:55,134 --> 01:57:57,034
I promised to bring Frank
back to Hong Kong

1161
01:58:00,239 --> 01:58:01,069
I kept my words!

1162
01:58:03,709 --> 01:58:04,869
I bring him home!

1163
01:58:10,016 --> 01:58:10,641
Ben are you out of your mind

1164
01:58:10,783 --> 01:58:12,876
When I saw him in Saigon he was crazy
He lived like animal, he led a dog's life!

1165
01:58:13,019 --> 01:58:13,781
You know why?

1166
01:58:15,755 --> 01:58:17,222
Because he got a bullet in his head!

1167
01:58:25,264 --> 01:58:26,993
Why didn't you shoot straight?

1168
01:58:29,368 --> 01:58:30,596
Now he has to suffer more?

1169
01:58:33,339 --> 01:58:35,398
Is it worth it to kill a friend
for a box of gold?

1170
01:58:35,942 --> 01:58:37,034
There are dead people lying
all over the place in wartime

1171
01:58:37,243 --> 01:58:39,768
You can bring back any bone
and said it belongs to Frank!

1172
02:01:55,708 --> 02:01:57,699
You want to get a revenge? Damn it!

1173
02:01:59,845 --> 02:02:01,107
I never lose in my life...

1174
02:02:01,580 --> 02:02:03,241
They did not kill me in Vietnam,
you think you can scare me now?

1175
02:02:04,216 --> 02:02:05,877
We are all fugitives in our lives,
see who run out of our luck first!

1176
02:02:18,197 --> 02:02:19,221
You're going to lose, Paul

1177
02:02:19,932 --> 02:02:22,423
Don't worry, I never lose in my life

1178
02:06:51,337 --> 02:06:54,465
Ben, we must die together

1179
02:07:07,086 --> 02:07:09,247
Frank, shut up

1180
02:07:14,627 --> 02:07:19,223
You bring it yourself, you are a dead man
You dare follow me

1181
02:07:20,399 --> 02:07:23,596
You want to rest in peace

1182
02:07:25,938 --> 02:07:30,307
Let me help you

1183
02:07:32,811 --> 02:07:34,745
I'm going to take the box of gold!

1184
02:07:36,515 --> 02:07:38,380
Do you envy?

1185
02:07:57,503 --> 02:08:00,199
You don't have a long life to enjoy it

1186
02:08:01,573 --> 02:08:03,404
Let me help you to rest in peace

1187
02:08:06,979 --> 02:08:08,810
He said he wanted to rest in peace
What shall we do?

1188
02:08:09,381 --> 02:08:11,372
Give him one more shoot to help him
Come on, help your friend

1189
02:08:11,583 --> 02:08:12,140
Shoot him!

1190
02:08:15,854 --> 02:08:17,754
Give him one more shoot!
So that he can rest in peace!

1191
02:08:18,390 --> 02:08:19,516
And he can't follow us

1192
02:08:20,626 --> 02:08:22,992
Shoot, Ben! Help him to rest in peace!

1193
02:08:24,029 --> 02:08:25,326
Then we won't suffer anymore

1194
02:08:31,770 --> 02:08:32,600
I can continue to earn money

1195
02:08:34,206 --> 02:08:35,605
You can make some new friends

1196
02:08:35,808 --> 02:08:38,436
Shoot him!

